videos.description: Justin Gray's two-handed tip-in bucket caps a 13-0 run for Texas Tech.
videos.headline: Gray tips it in on the fast break

videos.description: Zach Smith receives the pass from Norense Odiase and finishes with a two-handed dunk for the Red Raiders.
videos.headline: Smith with a royal-flush slam dunk

videos.description: Zach Smith rejects the shot attempt of Kennesaw State's Jake Scott and sends it into the stands.
videos.headline: Smith with a nasty shot block

videos.description: Nick Masterson drives and feeds to Jordan Jones for a dunk for Kennesaw State.
videos.headline: Jones with a two-handed slam dunk

videos.description: Niem Stevenson get the handoff, drives the lane for a right-handed dunk for Texas Tech.
videos.headline: Stevenson parts the sea and dunks it home

videos.description: Justin Gray gets the loose ball, runs the floor and finishes with a front-faced dunk.
videos.headline: Gray with a breakaway dunk

videos.description: Texas Tech's Zhaire Smith dunks it home for the finish.
videos.headline: Smith joins the dunk party

videos.description: Davide Moretti loses control of the ball but manages to gain back the possession, then lobs it up to Zhaire Smith, who finishes with an alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Smith dunks cross-court, alley-oop feed
